title: Official Teaser - Moche Rip Curl Pro Portugal 2013
description:
We searched and we stayed, and why wouldn't we? Pumping waves and an epic place with awesome people. Join us this October for non-stop action as the world's best surfers pull into on of the world's best beach breaks. As the second last stop on the ASP World Tour, we're expecting breathtaking moments and bone crushing defeats as we near the crowning of the 2013 ASP World Champion. Watch live on ripcurl.com.

Music: Sparklepussy Barbie
Track: Ocean
Source: Getty Images
